</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Pediatric Ophthalmology Provider and Staff Attitudes and Patient Satisfaction in Telehealth Implementation During COVID-19</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Summers%20AI"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Allison I Summers</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Allison I Summers</span>, <span class="degrees">OD, MCR</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup><sup>1</sup></sup>Elks Children's Eye Clinic, Casey Eye Institute, Oregon Health and Science University, Portland, Oregon, USA.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Summers%20AI"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Allison I Summers</span></a>
</div>
