<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Loh%20AR"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">Allison R Loh</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Allison R Loh</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup><sup>1</sup></sup>Elks Children's Eye Clinic, Casey Eye Institute, Oregon Health and Science University, Portland, Oregon, USA.</div>
