<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Brinks%20MV"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Mitchell V Brinks</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>2</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Hribar%20MR"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id6"><span class="name western">Michelle R Hribar</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id6">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Michelle R Hribar</span>, <span class="degrees">PhD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup><sup>3</sup></sup>Department of Medical Informatics and Clinical Epidemiology, Casey Eye Institute, Oregon Health and Science University, Portland, Oregon, USA.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Hribar%20MR"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Michelle R Hribar</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>3</sup>
</div>
<ul class="d-buttons inline-list">
<li><button class="d-button" aria-controls="aip_a" aria-expanded="false">Author information</button></li>
<li><button class="d-button" aria-controls="anp_a" aria-expanded="false">Article notes</button></li>
